tv.amwa.maj.constant

Interface PluginCategoryType


  • public interface PluginCategoryType

    Implement this interface to access unique identifiers describing the categories of plugin. This interface is also used to seed the define the extendible enumeration PluginCategoryType.

    See Also:
    ExtendibleEnumerationItem, TypeDefinitionExtendibleEnumeration, PluginDefinition.getCategoryClass(), Warehouse.lookupExtendibleEnumeration(String), TypeDefinitions.PluginCategoryType

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static AUID Codec
      Specifies that a plugin that provides the implementation of a codec, such as the codecs described by the codec identifiers.
      static AUID Effect
      Specifies that a plugin that provides the implementation of an effect, such as the effects described by the operation identifiers.
      static AUID Interpolation
      Specifies that a plugin that provides the implementation of an interpolation function, such as the interpolation functions described by the interpolation identifiers.
